When adding interaction terms,

00:00:33.710 --> 00:00:37.640
you're considering it the way that a variable X1 is related to your response Y,

00:00:37.640 --> 00:00:41.070
is dependent on another variable X2.

00:00:41.070 --> 00:00:43.009
As an example, consider

