00:01:19.569 --> 00:01:24.804
However, imagine if the relationship actually looked like this for neighborhood B.

00:01:24.805 --> 00:01:27.635
Here, we can see that the slopes of these two lines

00:01:27.635 --> 00:01:30.935
no longer match in order to account for this,

00:01:30.935 --> 00:01:33.200
we would want to add an interaction term between

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:36.545
