00:01:49.120 --> 00:01:51.620
So the question of adding an interaction is a question

00:01:51.620 --> 00:01:54.454
about these slopes being close enough to equal.

00:01:54.454 --> 00:01:56.569
If the slopes are close to equal,

00:01:56.569 --> 00:01:58.524
